list.comment: - Fixed a bug, where when you updated a c2mon configuration and created a new equipment, the data tags would not get created

- started refreshAllDataTags();
- updated C2monService
- Created ModbusTCPService
- Bug fix / enhancements
- started parsing XML config from C2mon server - bug fix
- Bug fixes and XML deserialization and enhancements and and and
- Bug fixes and XML deserialization and enhancements and and and
- Edited Dockerfile and enabled Docker support - Fixed bug "JMS Message Error" - Static ModbusTCPService for testing purposes
- Enabled Docker Maven caching - Filled the methods refreshDataTag() and refreshAllDataTags() - edited config file

- Fixed bug where the second value update did not work - Changed version of DAQParent from 1.9.8 to 1.10.0 - Loading configuration from equipment configuration - Hardware address handling from ModbusTCPService -> DAQMessageHandler
- Removed old code fragments - Removed unused code fragments - Code clean up - Additional JavaDoc - Removed custom start method and replaced it with the default - Changed logging level to 'info'
- Support of multiple equipments in yaml configuration

- Automatically load configuration file and configure the C2mon server - Force configuration option -> overwrite the existing configuration on C2mon server - Deleted C2monService.java and moved all necessary functionality to ConfigService.java - Created a ConfigInitializer which administrates the configuration and reconfiguration of the C2mon server - Switched back to custom start method in main class because otherwise Spring services are not loaded

- If force reconfiguration is false: - automatically update configuration - no deletion of process / equipments / datatags - creation of new process / equipments / datatags if the ConfigInitializer does not find the one, specified in config - set default alive tag interval to 100000ms (100s)
- Added JavaDoc for all relevant methods - Removed unused methods - Cleaned up code - Warning if force update is not specified
- logging change

- Loading Yaml config from external sources - Automatic reconnection to modbus endpoint - added offset - added multiplier - added threshold - performance increase with caching - bug fix - enhancements
- Added optionality to load demo config - Preparations for including command tags - Added data type attribute to command tag
- CommandTag implementation - BitNumber implementation
- Loading multiple equipments from config file - code clean up - bug fix

- If refresh delay is not specified in c2mon xml, due to an older daq version, setting a default which amounts 10000ms - 'c2mon.daq.refreshInterval' environmental variable is no longer supported, config file has to be used - Better handling if something is misspelled in the config file - Removed model settings from config (unnecessary) - Better logging
- Added GeneralSettings to config file - Version 1.0.0
- Config file: 'count' option not longer necessary, 'holding', 'holding32' & 'holding64' distinction not longer needed, just use 'holding' - Version 1.0.0
